layout: base.njk
title: Blogroll
permalink: /blogroll/
---

<h2>Blogs and sites I enjoy reading</h2>

Curating and getting into the habit of checking a blogroll has been a really
useful substitute for high-frutose corn syrup social media consumption.

<hr/>

<div class="blog-layout">
    {% if blogrollPosts.length %}
  <div class="blog-main">
    <p>Recent posts</p>
    <ul class="blogroll-posts">
      {%- for post in blogrollPosts %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.title }}</a>
        <span class="blogroll-meta">— {{ post.source }}, {{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
      </li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

    <aside class="blog-sidebar">
        <p>Sources</p>
          {%- for entry in blogroll %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ entry.url }}">{{ entry.name }}</a>
          </li>
          {%- endfor %}
    </aside>
    {% endif %}
</div>
